{"tid":2501530,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV首度與HBO合作拍劇  網民睇完預告大讚期待","createTime":"2021-04-23T12:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T14:33:30.000Z","uid":350584,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b1a7ec95dc4b75b17bed40a21b8e05107cc33c","tid":2501530,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"在去年7月，MIRROR的成員邱士縉（Stanley）飛往台灣拍劇，但當時他未有提及拍甚麼劇，只表示並非與姜濤合作，在將來的日子，希望在演員方向定位。原來Stanley今次與金鐘視帝莊凱勛、金馬獎男配角劉冠廷和影后張榕容合演劇集《第三佈局塵沙惑》，劇集將於6月13日在HBO頻道、HBO GO及CATCHPLAY+影音平台同步首播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qQ-WX-YSulvZxvkbZq0IUxsjNlw=/487x273/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OZ5ZVYM6UFBCTEN4AGQHKXP5XE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqQ-WX-YSulvZxvkbZq0IUxsjNlw%3D%2F487x273%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOZ5ZVYM6UFBCTEN4AGQHKXP5XE.jpg&h=55a17c4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a361fe456052109b628efd357f6e487eb59eb64a","tid":2501530,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:13:40.000Z","msg":"故事由一宗分屍案揭開序幕，經調查後發現案件竟與23年前的謀殺案有關聯，在調查過程中，他們被捲入佈局之中。昨日官方發放了一段預告片，聽到劉冠廷聲嘶力竭吶喊的對白：「那些口口聲聲要別人放下仇恨的人，他們真的知道仇恨是甚麼嗎？」已經相當有震撼的感覺。"},{"pid":"07d9a08c24fac589c46fccf05d482625bca19ce5","tid":2501530,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"預告片都唔 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a27d3562236737f33f103c55baef31e53743736","tid":2501530,"uid":350584,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"不過最值得一提的事，《第三佈局塵沙惑》是ViuTV第一部台灣作品，與華納傳媒及CATCHPLAY聯合出品，雖然過往ViuTV曾經與愛奇藝合作拍《嘆息橋》，不過今時今日與大陸合作拍合拍劇，已經是平常不過的事，但今次ViuTV與HBO合作，再加上台前幕後的班底強勁，所以消息一出，已經有不少網民表示期待：「唔知道ViuTV幾時可以有得睇！」「HBO 合作開嗰啲差唔多全部都好高質素！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/o8BPPaN_IIqzmjjZ1Eu3D846qoA=/487x273/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2GIXNSFPLZBCLPUAMZLJJGEGAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fo8BPPaN_IIqzmjjZ1Eu3D846qoA%3D%2F487x273%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2GIXNSFPLZBCLPUAMZLJJGEGAY.jpg&h=d061a7a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2fc56e1cf6e6967db793ff06e668aa0706106d9","tid":2501530,"uid":95520,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:15:41.000Z","msg":"網民有冇睇過太平紋身店嘅預告"},{"pid":"913faaa69a015cff67cfbeb7e10d5ce99cfc8e23","tid":2501530,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"07d9a08c24fac589c46fccf05d482625bca19ce5","tid":2501530,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"預告片都唔 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=HODLI4Rgbm8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHODLI4Rgbm8&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=aa6da792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=HODLI4Rgbm8</a>"},{"pid":"b526ee201136a1257566bfccdc63a61d8eabf136","tid":2501530,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a27d3562236737f33f103c55baef31e53743736","tid":2501530,"uid":350584,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"不過最值得一提的事，《第三佈局塵沙惑》是ViuTV第一部台灣作品，與華納傳媒及CATCHPLAY聯合出品，雖然過往ViuTV曾經與愛奇藝合作拍《嘆息橋》，不過今時今日與大陸合作拍合拍劇，已經是平常不過的事，但今次ViuTV與HBO合作，再加上台前幕後的班底強勁，所以消息一出，已經有不少網民表示期待：「唔知道ViuTV幾時可以有得睇！」「HBO 合作開嗰啲差唔多全部都好高質素！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/o8BPPaN_IIqzmjjZ1Eu3D846qoA=/487x273/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2GIXNSFPLZ